ParetoSolution - Class in fr.polytechtours.prd.multiagent.model
This class is defined as the representation of one pareto solution
Three elements are included in this class: sequence: list of ids of jobs which are able to be scheduled valueObjA: the value of the objective function for agent A valueObjB: the value of the objective function for agent B The order of domination is also defined by implementing the interface Comparable
If one pareto solution dominates another one, the method compareTo return -1
hashCode() and equals() are overrided.
